    "name": "delivery pals",
    "steam_appid": 3237570,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/ef7a4c4111fbb4fd3f12cf2a6a76af33.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=65 /></span>地球已经灭亡。很久以前，人类就因为地球变得无法居住而离开了。如今，这里充满了腐蚀性的环境、大量怪物和异常现象。唯一还会光顾地球的智慧生物是外星人，他们对人类的食物情有独钟。<br><br>你将扮演猫咪快递员。你的目标是通过送餐赚取金钱，保持公司盈利。然而，人类会竭尽全力关闭你的公司，提高你的任务配额，并消灭地球上的所有生命，包括你。<br><br>你只有一个任务：<strong>生存！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/cc68884ddc57cc50f407d7cfd886a9fe.poster.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/cc68884ddc57cc50f407d7cfd886a9fe.webm?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/cc68884ddc57cc50f407d7cfd886a9fe.mp4?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/b092f61af99e9999b6454438faf32307.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;你和你的朋友们拥有一辆超级快速的改装列车，用它进行移动。&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>&quot;列车上还包括：&quot;</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商店 – 出售在地表找到的没用垃圾，你用不上它们。最好买几节电池和一个手电筒以防万一。还有，别忘了对讲机！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ATM – 存款、取款、给你的朋友转账，或者支付配额。所有的金融操作都在这里完成！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电脑终端 – 设置列车的目的地，处理食物订单，或者阅读员工手册。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摄像头监控器 – 通过胸前摄像头或卫星摄像头观察你的朋友。在能见度差的情况下提前提醒他们危险。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冰箱 – 把不需要的食物存放在这里，防止丢失。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厨房桌 – 如果订单需要的东西在最近的垃圾桶里没找到，也许你可以自己做出来？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球雷达 – 查看所有当前订单及其编号，然后在终端中处理它们。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/55c444dec308c0b9b7fe45bdf9b7d524.poster.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/55c444dec308c0b9b7fe45bdf9b7d524.webm?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/55c444dec308c0b9b7fe45bdf9b7d524.mp4?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/8a3bc3beede13f99d8b3597546dbda78.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=65 /></span>本游戏设计为与朋友一起玩，最多支持 7 名玩家。建议邀请至少 2 个朋友！不过，你也可以加入公开游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/20371b01337af1075c01dd77df826ed6.poster.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/20371b01337af1075c01dd77df826ed6.webm?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/20371b01337af1075c01dd77df826ed6.mp4?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/68e7f4e15b26213fac07b86865047553.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=65 /></span>开始你的旅程吧！处理订单并找到正确的食物完成送餐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食物或烹饪材料可以在垃圾袋、容器中找到，或者例如你可以从鸟巢里偷一个蛋，做个炒蛋！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心，如果你弄错了订单，送错了食物，外星人会攻击你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/17f00c1794384f64a57cc305254f39ee.poster.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/17f00c1794384f64a57cc305254f39ee.webm?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/17f00c1794384f64a57cc305254f39ee.mp4?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/d2ec62bf588fefe1fd44098e2be7ae0f.poster.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/d2ec62bf588fefe1fd44098e2be7ae0f.webm?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/d2ec62bf588fefe1fd44098e2be7ae0f.mp4?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/585ab0bd5d6a552cc8a215dbfbece379.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=65 /></span>随意组合你的工具，每只手都可以拿着一样东西。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/6676d01b6318b13cd8441acb69549394.poster.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/6676d01b6318b13cd8441acb69549394.webm?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/6676d01b6318b13cd8441acb69549394.mp4?t=1753801210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237570/extras/40a5c6f1a5b4f5aa47e05742b22324b9.avif?t=1753801210\" width=800 height=65 /></span></p>",
